N'omenala ndị Aborigine nke ndịda ọwụwa anyanwụ mba Australia, Daramulum (ọdịiche: Darhumulan, Daramulan, Dhurramoolun ma ọ bụ Dharramaalan) bụ dike igwe jikọtara ya na Baiame, na emu-nwunye. Ọ bụ onye na-agbanwe ọdịdị.
Ihe osise nke Daramulum na-esonyere mgbe ụfọdụ na indentations nke nwere ike ịnọchite anya ìgwè kpakpando.

A na-egosi Daramulum na ihe osise nkume na Elvina Track na Ku-ring-gai Chase National Park, nso ihe a tụrụ atụ nke nwunye ya. A na-egosi ya na ọkara profaịlụ, nwere otu ogwe aka, emu-azụ (ya bụ, ogwe aka dị nkọ), na nnukwu ụkwụ.
Enwere ike ịnụ olu ya site na ụda nke bullroarer nke a na-agbagharị na ikuku n'oge emume mmalite
Ọ na-ebi ugbu a n'osisi nke ọhịa, ọkachasị na burls ma ọ bụ uto nke a na-ahụ na ogwe osisi, ma hapụ ha naanị maka emume mmalite
A ghaghị ịkpụpụ bullroarer site n'osisi nke nwere mmụọ ya ka ọ rụọ ọrụ
Maka Guringai, Alpha Crucis nke Southern Cross na-anọchite anya Daramulum, ebe ihe fọdụrụ na Cross na- nnọchite anya isi nke nwunye ya emu (nke emu na kpakpando igwe).
